  <titles>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Opportunity for Military Academies and Readiness Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">To amend title 10, United States Code, to authorize aliens who have been granted deferred action and work authorization under the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals program of the Department of Homeland Security and who otherwise satisfy the requirements for admission to a military service academy to be appointed to and attend a military service academy and, upon graduation, to be appointed as a commissioned officer in the Armed Forces.</title>
